2026-05-10T20:33:24.8695356Z 238        <!--
2026-05-10T20:33:24.8695705Z 239            Override Google Play Billing's ProxyBillingActivity so the system
2026-05-10T20:33:24.8696020Z 240            cannot restore it from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-10T20:33:24.8696337Z 241            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-10T20:33:24.8696903Z 242            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-10T20:33:24.8697117Z 243            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-10T20:33:24.8697465Z 244            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-10T20:33:24.8697774Z 245            ensures the activity is finished as soon as it leaves the
2026-05-10T20:33:24.8698082Z 246            foreground and is never re-entered with a missing extra. See
2026-05-10T20:33:24.8698399Z 247            crash report tagged "ProxyBillingActivity NPE" for context.
